{"tid":2494453,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"日本核廢水重點唔係氚 係碳14、鈷60、鍶90","createTime":"2021-04-18T15:03:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T06:29:13.000Z","uid":98232,"like":8,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc8fa053fc1d278e238a8a4f20879e7f7aa77d4","tid":2494453,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:03:47.000Z","msg":"正視聽 個個都淨係講氚 <br />\n氚確實日常生活好常見對人體傷害唔大<br />\n半衰期亦好短<br />\n日本用alps淨化技術根本淨化唔到碳14<br />\n仲有ken buesseler係science發表過日本<br />\n處理後既核廢水除左氚超標<br />\n仲有碳14、鈷60、鍶90<br />\n但日本從來無提過仲有碳14、鈷60、鍶90超標<br />\n碳14半衰期5730萬年<br />\n鈷60半衰萬5年<br />\n鍶90半衰期29年<br />\n但鈷同鍶呢2種最易被人體骨頭同腎吸收"},{"pid":"5143810aa84fc345c8eb9fe1a100bbf710d72b6e","tid":2494453,"uid":98232,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:15:59.000Z","msg":"連登仔個個盲撚左"},{"pid":"15761e7c1f9318c9c39dfa3a419f1ba454c5e1b0","tid":2494453,"uid":59839,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:17:01.000Z","msg":"有冇超標?"},{"pid":"be9310866f3e41ae4340604851355fe5b992fe8c","tid":2494453,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"15761e7c1f9318c9c39dfa3a419f1ba454c5e1b0","tid":2494453,"uid":59839,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:17:01.000Z","msg":"有冇超標?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:18:34.000Z","msg":"ken buesseler係science<br />\n發表過文章過係海水中搵到呢幾種放射性原素"},{"pid":"aeca116426b751d465963869edf6dacc7e46117f","tid":2494453,"uid":179824,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"be9310866f3e41ae4340604851355fe5b992fe8c","tid":2494453,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"15761e7c1f9318c9c39dfa3a419f1ba454c5e1b0","tid":2494453,"uid":59839,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:17:01.000Z","msg":"有冇超標?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:18:34.000Z","msg":"ken buesseler係science<br />\n發表過文章過係海水中搵到呢幾種放射性原素"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:20:18.000Z","msg":"姐係本身exist?<img src=\"/asse