子（半衰期&ge;8d）3.80E+09Bq<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">  碳14 2.20E+12Bq</span><br />\n<br />\n  气态氚2.40E+13Bq<br />\n<br />\n  液体放射性流出物：碳14 3.00E+11Bq<br />\n<br />\n  液态氚2.25E+14Bq<br />\n<br />\n  <span class=\"red\">其余核素1.30E+11Bq</span><br />\n<br />\n  你公司应根据《核动力厂环境辐射防护规定》（GB 6249－2011）的要求，每隔5年对流出物年排放量限值进行重新评估，并报我局复核。<br />\n<br />\n  国家核安全局<br />\n<br />\n  2017年7月1"},{"pid":"0afa066a1106dea0573c39115eeee3e4fe1db469","tid":2494453,"uid":119393,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8fc8fa053fc1d278e238a8a4f20879e7f7aa77d4","tid":2494453,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:03:47.000Z","msg":"正視聽 個個都淨係講氚 <br />\n氚確實日常生活好常見對人體傷害唔大<br />\n半衰期亦好短<br />\n日本用alps淨化技術根本淨化唔到碳14<br />\n仲有ken buesseler係science發表過日本<br />\n處理後既核廢水除左氚超標<br />\n仲有碳14、鈷60、鍶90<br />\n但日本從來無提過仲有碳14、鈷60、鍶90超標<br />\n碳14半衰期5730萬年<br />\n鈷60半衰萬5年<br />\n鍶90半衰期29年<br />\n但鈷同鍶呢2種最易被人體骨頭同腎吸收"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"正視聽<br />\n我見好多人關心碳14<br />\n就試下用中日官方數字計埋碳14<br />\n日本核廢水平均每公升42.5Bq碳14<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXCS7AzhkASX3KD4mo96e1P9L1k3EyeWiq86z359MaSbd?filename=50YbdM0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50YbdM0.jpg&h=a6c42f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kr.emb-japan.go.jp/people/news/jisin_QnA_jp.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kr.emb-japan.go.jp%2Fpeople%2Fnews%2Fjisin_QnA_jp.html&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVprZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=b72f748d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kr.emb-japan.go.jp/people/news/jisin_QnA_jp.html</a><br />\n<br />\n截至3月核廢水一共125萬噸<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sankei.com/affairs/news/210310/afr2103100004-n1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sankei.com%2Faffairs%2Fnews%2F210310%2Fafr2103100004-n1.html&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVprZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=72320136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sankei.com/affairs/news/210310/afr2103100004-n1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n即係所有核廢水夾埋有<br />\n42.5*約1000*1,250,000<br />\n=約53,125,000,000Bq碳14<br />\n如果按計劃分30年排放<br />\n一年排放 =1,770,833,333Bq碳14<br />\n<br />\n根據大亞灣核電廠官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hknuclear.com/DayaPerf/Releases/Pages/Radioactive.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hknuclear.com%2FDayaPerf%2FReleases%2FPages%2FRadioactive.aspx&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVprZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=e158f00d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hknuclear.com/DayaPerf/Releases/Pages/Radioactive.aspx</a><br />\n大亞灣液態碳14一年排放上限300GBq<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU7BpzeJAGJ1VCDiFR4cjwCWCoqvAvbaasKaLjJrEhehT?filename=y4WL2Nv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4WL2Nv.jpg&h=529f5548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n300GBq=300MBq*1000=300KBq*1000^2=300Bq*1000^3<br />\n=300,000,000,000Bq碳14<br />\n如上圖, 2020年大亞灣排放了上限6.18%的液態碳14<br />\n=18,540,000,000Bq碳14<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n大亞灣核電廠於2020年排出大海的碳14(氣態先唔計)<br />\n是福島核廢水排放計劃中每年排放碳14的12倍以上<br />\n大亞灣只是中國其中兩個核反應堆<br />\n中國沿海有約40個核反應堆"},{"pid":"71266feb984fefefd0b417e5f5f0bf0d3e1546ea","tid":2494453,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0afa066a1106dea0573c39115eeee3e4fe1db469","tid":2494453,"uid":119393,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8fc8fa053fc1d278e238a8a4f20879e7f7aa77d4","tid":2494453,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:03:47.000Z","msg":"正視聽 個個都淨係講氚 <br />\n氚確實日常生活好常見對人體傷害唔大<br />\n半衰期亦好短<br />\n日本用alps淨化技術根本淨化唔到碳14<br />\n仲有ken buesseler係science發表過日本<br />\n處理後既核廢水除左氚超標<br />\n仲有碳14、鈷60、鍶90<br />\n但日本從來無提過仲有碳14、鈷60、鍶90超標<br />\n碳14半衰期5730萬年<br />\n鈷60半衰萬5年<br />\n鍶90半衰期29年<br />\n但鈷同鍶呢2種最易被人體骨頭同腎吸收"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"正視聽<br />\n我見好多人關心碳14<br />\n就試下用中日官方數字計埋碳14<br />\n日本核廢水平均每公升42.5Bq碳14<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50YbdM0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=